{"tid":803004,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"淡淡們，我當你樓價跌八成，返返去海嘯價前，咁又有乜大不了姐？","createTime":"2018-09-02T01:49:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T01:26:47.000Z","uid":147097,"like":30,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"7aa5ba03effa952334964567dcc2565db4dd93d8","tid":803004,"uid":147097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T01:49:05.000Z","msg":"樓價大升因為ＱＥ<br />\n<br />\n而家縮表，大不了返返去海嘯前<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nＣＡＳＥ１<br />\n而家有晒壓測，最多咪供三十年<br />\n<br />\n好多人成副身家扑晒落去，食屎都會供落去啦，最多咪食三十年屎？<br />\n<br />\nＣＡＳＥ２<br />\n最壞情況咪比人CALL LOAN<br />\n<br />\n渣都無又點? 五年後又一條好漢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n樓價跌八成又點? SO WHAT? 有乜咁大不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53008b6948c40ee20b3ba14c8383aee06f1b78c6","tid":803004,"uid":190540,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T02:09:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"38bd90405e278c861a53e783700dd7c386ad2808","tid":803004,"uid":84275,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T02:28:08.000Z","msg":"你up乜鳩，跌8成我份首期變fullpay啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e0b15d1f4173eb8735d11c71eae967fd8e49817","tid":803004,"uid":126621,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T02:41:40.000Z","msg":"call loan 要跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今年買完樓結婚生完仔<br />\n下年同你講無左層樓仲要爭銀行300萬<br />\n<br />\n成家一齊跳"},{"pid":"efbc9273c1be0665bbff71952c7385c4f680207a","tid":803004,"uid":57309,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"38bd90405e278c861a53e783700dd7c386ad2808","tid":803004,"uid":84275,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T02:28:08.000Z","msg":"你up乜鳩，跌8成我份首期變fullpay啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class